<arggraph id="micro_k031" topic_id="higher_dog_poo_fines" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Pieces of dog poo on the pavements are a real danger.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[Time and again children or the elderly slip on them.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[A fine for leaving dog waste behind admittedly seems rather authoritarian,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[but similar rules are often in place for bicycles on park paths, after all.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Increasing penalties is therefore the right way.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[A dog dirt-free city will be more attractive not only for its residents but also for tourists!]]></edu>
